{"id":"designmd-chrome-ext-nxb","title":"designmd-chrome-ext: Enhanced Design System Extractor","description":"Build a Chrome extension that captures design tokens and generates DESIGN.md files using AI vision, with improved reliability, richer UI, and persistent history.\n\n## Goals\n- Full-page screenshot + AI vision analysis\n- Design token extraction (colors, typography, spacing, etc.)\n- Google Stitch-compatible DESIGN.md output\n- History persistence with IndexedDB\n- Enhanced UI with preview, cancel, progress\n\n## Tech Stack\n- Manifest V3 Chrome Extension\n- Vanilla JS/CSS (no framework)\n- IndexedDB for history\n- OffscreenCanvas for screenshot stitching\n\n## Scope\nSee project milestones for breakdown.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","owner":"75532567+0xzapata@users.noreply.github.com","created_at":"2026-05-02T02:39:06Z","created_by":"Niel","updated_at":"2026-05-02T02:39:06Z","dependency_count":0,"dependent_count":4,"comment_count":0}
